Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:11.15,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Why are My Melody and I\Nacting all chummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.78,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,Is she not your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.02,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.38,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,We're {\i1}rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.60,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Oh? When did you get over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.31,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,M-M-M-My Melody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:21.69,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.15,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:25.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I ain't your world's Kuro—hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.36,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Hey! You can't tell strangers\Nabout the extended universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.19,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I-I mean, sure, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.77,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Wait up, little butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:36.85,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.65,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:38.85,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Bah-hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:41.60,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Kuromi, say "ahh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.60,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Bah...{nyo}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.69,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Kuromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.02,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Is it yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:45.85,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.94,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Could this be kawaii chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I'm actually having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.52,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I really should get home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:55.90,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made everyone really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:58.90,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Wanna play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.60,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Baw, if I have to, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.69,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,You're such a sweetheart, Kuromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.31,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I... am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.27,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:12.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I'm only running for myself,\Nnot for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:14.44,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,It's all so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:18.56,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,But I have lots more fun when you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:19.31,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.44,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I guess... I should go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:25.60,RiskySubs,My Melody,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.52,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I'm on my way, guys.
